---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import caltaraCity from "../assets/CaltaraCity.jpg";
---

<section id="city" class="relative min-h-[900px] w-full overflow-hidden bg-[var(--color-obsidian)] py-20 sm:py-0">
  <Image
    src={caltaraCity}
    alt="Caltara, capital of the Caltaran Republic"
    class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover object-center"
    widths={[640, 1024, 1294]}
    sizes="100vw"
  />

  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[var(--color-obsidian)] via-[var(--color-obsidian)]/20 to-transparent"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[var(--color-obsidian)]/05 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grain"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 flex min-h-[900px] items-end px-6 py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="panel-carved glow-hover max-w-2xl p-8 sm:p-10 animate-rise">
      <span class="corner-ornament tl"></span>
      <span class="corner-ornament tr"></span>
      <span class="corner-ornament bl"></span>
      <span class="corner-ornament br"></span>

      <p class="eyebrow">Capital of the Republic</p>
      <h2 class="mt-4 font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-[var(--color-parchment)] tracking-wide">
        Caltara
      </h2>

      <div class="mt-5 space-y-4 text-[var(--color-parchment-dim)] leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Caltara is the capital of the <span class="text-[var(--color-gold-bright)]">Caltaran Republic</span>,
          and one of the three original city-states that signed the
          <span class="text-[var(--color-gold-bright)]"> Covenant of White Shores</span>.
          The name passed from city to nation gradually people
          started calling the Republic after its capital out of convenience,
          and convenience became convention. The Republic's official name is
          still the Caltaran Republic. Most people just say Caltara.
        </p>
        <p>
          It is the seat of both Senates, the largest city in the Republic,
          and where most of what matters politically gets decided, in
          the Open Senate's chamber, the harbor-district coffee houses, the
          counting rooms of the old guild houses, and whatever room the
          Closed Senate uses for the conversations that never appear in any
          public record.
        </p>

      </div>

      <a
        href="/caltara"
        class="mt-7 inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-display text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[var(--color-gold)] hover:text-[var(--color-gold-bright)] border-b border-[var(--color-gold-dim)] pb-1 transition-colors"
      >
        Discover Caltara &rarr;
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
